A tearful farewell 🥹

Moving to another place , its scary but also exciting !! 
But this was our first biggest shift from Ahmedabad to Nadiad , new city new people!! 

This studio has mostly seen the highest growth of C&B , it has seen the hardest harwork , it has seen  tears, it has seen tonnes of orders and it also saw silence.

This will be the hardest goodbye but B-59 you will always be remembered as a part of our biggest change so far ♥️🥰

Goodbye ✨🫰🏻
